com.dooapp.gaedo.blueprints
Interface GraphDatabaseDriver

public interface GraphDatabaseDriver

Graph database interface allows classical operations on graph, viewed as a database : finding vertices, updating them, and so on ... For those knowing old versions of gaedo-blueprints (0.2 branch), it's the equivalent of the GraphUtils class.

Author:
ndx

loadVertexFor

com.tinkerpop.blueprints.pgm.Vertex loadVertexFor(String objectVertexId,
                                                  String className)
Load vertex having the given id. Relationship between id and vertex is dependant upon graph implementation : id may be stored as a property, or it can be an URI ...

Parameters:
objectVertexId - a string id
className - the class this vertex should be associated with
Returns:
vertex corresponding to that id ... or an exception if none found
